1
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:00,000
"School Trip: Joined a Group I'm Not Close to" - After Story

2
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:05,500
(Part 1: Can't Catch My Breath)

3
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:09,899
Three months into my
relationship with Watarai...

4
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,296
(Tsujitani, please!)
- Come on, it has to be... - Please! Please!

5
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:17,770
I'm facing a huge problem right now.

6
00:01:18,980 --> 00:01:20,999
It all started two months ago.

7
00:01:24,169 --> 00:01:25,479
I'm doomed.

8
00:01:26,660 --> 00:01:28,706
(New Semester - Junior Year Class Placements)
Hey! We've gotta be in the same class.

9
00:01:28,730 --> 00:01:30,030
We're in the same class again.

10
00:01:31,660 --> 00:01:33,213
(#21: Asahi Hioki)

11
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:35,700
Yes!

12
00:01:40,739 --> 00:01:42,039
We're...

13
00:01:42,129 --> 00:01:43,439
We're classmates this year.

14
00:01:44,510 --> 00:01:45,710
Let's make it a good year.

15
00:01:45,930 --> 00:01:46,930
Yeah.

16
00:01:48,870 --> 00:01:51,260
Oh, and Utsumi's here too.

17
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:52,639
Koseki.

18
00:01:52,975 --> 00:01:54,069
There's me...

19
00:01:55,070 --> 00:01:56,666
The junior year class
assignments were posted.

20
00:01:56,690 --> 00:01:59,849
Watarai and I didn't
end up in the same class.

21
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:03,260
Oh?

22
00:02:06,639 --> 00:02:10,869
Now, compared to that...

23
00:02:12,259 --> 00:02:14,170
Who's the king?

24
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,630
Yes!

25
00:02:16,779 --> 00:02:18,060
I'm the king.

26
00:02:18,889 --> 00:02:21,080
Why are we playing the King's Game?

27
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:23,839
Wait a minute.
Do guys even play this game?

28
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,639
Isn't this something you play at mixers?

29
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:28,100
Ooh.

30
00:02:28,679 --> 00:02:30,249
Number one and number three.

31
00:02:32,539 --> 00:02:33,839
Let's see a Pocky kiss.

32
00:02:34,009 --> 00:02:35,009
Ooh.

33
00:02:35,830 --> 00:02:36,990
Number one is Asahina.

34
00:02:37,949 --> 00:02:38,949
Whoa.

35
00:02:39,350 --> 00:02:40,649
And number three is Hioki.

36
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:41,710
Whoa, hold on.

37
00:02:41,949 --> 00:02:43,246
Can we change it to something else?

38
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:45,645
- How about a forehead flick or something?
- No way, no way, no way.

39
00:02:45,669 --> 00:02:47,100
The king's command...

40
00:02:48,229 --> 00:02:49,470
is absolute.

41
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:59,050
Why are you so into this?

42
00:02:59,410 --> 00:03:00,520
This is the worst.

43
00:03:01,259 --> 00:03:02,259
At this moment...

44
00:03:02,320 --> 00:03:04,119
If Watarai were to see this...

45
00:03:05,729 --> 00:03:06,929
Come on!

46
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:16,189
What do you think you're doing?!

47
00:03:16,510 --> 00:03:18,410
Come on, hurry up!

48
00:03:18,889 --> 00:03:19,889
Ahh.

49
00:03:25,009 --> 00:03:26,869
We're inches apart...

50
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,080
Hioki!

51
00:03:33,989 --> 00:03:35,729
Shoot... this is bad.

52
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:38,450
Can you give me a hand with this?

53
00:03:40,619 --> 00:03:43,179
What terrible timing...

54
00:03:48,130 --> 00:03:49,330
This'll toughen you up.

55
00:04:02,779 --> 00:04:04,280
What happened just now...

56
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:06,759
He definitely saw that, didn't he?

57
00:04:08,369 --> 00:04:10,599
Can I put this here?

58
00:04:15,910 --> 00:04:18,050
Why'd you lock the door?

59
00:04:22,059 --> 00:04:23,569
So we won't be interrupted.

60
00:04:23,910 --> 00:04:24,910
Huh?

61
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:38,980
Just now.

62
00:04:39,329 --> 00:04:40,329
What were you doing?

63
00:04:42,420 --> 00:04:43,420
I knew it.

64
00:04:45,179 --> 00:04:48,360
It was... the King's Game.
It was Tsujitani's idea.

65
00:04:50,339 --> 00:04:51,339
Mmm.

66
00:04:52,109 --> 00:04:53,239
And then...

67
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,450
Whoever was king called out our numbers...

68
00:04:57,299 --> 00:04:58,739
and told us to do the Pocky kiss.

69
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:04,920
Are you mad?

70
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:08,920
Of course he is.

71
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:12,569
If I were Watarai...

72
00:05:12,890 --> 00:05:14,090
and I saw my boyfriend...

73
00:05:14,170 --> 00:05:15,580
doing that...

74
00:05:19,700 --> 00:05:22,720
I'm so sorry.

75
00:05:24,709 --> 00:05:25,850
What should I do?

76
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,456
In a situation like this...

77
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,410
what would you do?

78
00:05:32,739 --> 00:05:34,099
Um, well...

79
00:05:38,029 --> 00:05:39,409
Can I hug you?

80
00:05:41,859 --> 00:05:42,859
Sure.

81
00:05:55,359 --> 00:05:56,559
Is that all?

82
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,830
Ah, huh?

83
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,630
A ki...

84
00:06:05,649 --> 00:06:06,649
A kiss...

85
00:06:07,829 --> 00:06:08,829
is that okay too?

86
00:06:09,839 --> 00:06:10,839
Yeah.

87
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,849
When you're like this...

88
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:40,029
you're so cute. I love it.

89
00:06:44,570 --> 00:06:46,259
But if we weren't dating,

90
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,200
this would be more than enough...

91
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:59,190
W-Wait, hold on, wait!

92
00:07:41,470 --> 00:07:42,470
I'm sorry.

93
00:07:42,989 --> 00:07:43,989
Did you not like that?

94
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:45,730
No.

95
00:07:46,799 --> 00:07:48,039
It's not that I didn't like it.

96
00:07:56,049 --> 00:07:57,049
Um, well...

97
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:59,009
Will you forgive me?

98
00:08:00,579 --> 00:08:01,579
You know...

99
00:08:02,239 --> 00:08:03,580
about the King's Game.

100
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:05,960
There's nothing to forgive.

101
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,279
I wasn't even mad.

102
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:10,440
Huh?

103
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:12,220
Besides...

104
00:08:12,260 --> 00:08:14,079
I never said I was angry, did I?

105
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:19,140
Seriously? I'm so sorry.

106
00:08:20,709 --> 00:08:22,050
I thought you were mad.

107
00:08:22,859 --> 00:08:24,079
I just lost my head.

108
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,800
And I just kissed you.

109
00:08:27,459 --> 00:08:28,689
Lost your head, huh?

110
00:08:30,299 --> 00:08:31,299
For the record,

111
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,660
I'd rather you kiss me whenever you want.

112
00:08:34,388 --> 00:08:35,918
Whenever you want...?

113
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:38,120
Because I'm your boyfriend.

114
00:08:39,090 --> 00:08:40,090
Boy...

115
00:08:52,260 --> 00:08:53,260
But...

116
00:08:53,609 --> 00:08:55,440
I'm way more...

117
00:08:55,909 --> 00:08:57,029
impatient than you think.

118
00:08:58,599 --> 00:08:59,599
Really?

119
00:09:00,229 --> 00:09:01,229
If I wasn't,

120
00:09:01,419 --> 00:09:04,939
I wouldn't have gone out of my way to trade
for cleaning duty just to get you alone here.

121
00:09:05,330 --> 00:09:07,530
And I wouldn't have kissed you like that.

122
00:09:11,219 --> 00:09:12,779
Even though we're in different classes,

123
00:09:12,900 --> 00:09:14,510
my feelings for you haven't changed.

124
00:09:14,979 --> 00:09:16,499
In fact, they've gotten even stronger.

125
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:20,630
What am I supposed to do?

126
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:24,580
Um...

127
00:09:25,109 --> 00:09:26,330
I... I feel the same way.

128
00:09:31,296 --> 00:09:32,296
Oh, no.

129
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:35,430
I want to kiss you again.

130
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:36,880
Huh?

131
00:09:38,929 --> 00:09:41,479
B-But we've already
kissed so many times today.

132
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,039
What's wrong with that?

133
00:09:43,109 --> 00:09:44,109
Mmm.

134
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:50,836
Due to the approaching typhoon,

135
00:09:50,837 --> 00:09:52,849
classes are cancelled for the afternoon.

136
00:09:53,219 --> 00:09:56,789
Students who commute by bus or train
please head home as soon as possible.

137
00:10:04,749 --> 00:10:05,749
Hioki.

138
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,540
- How are you getting home?
- Huh?

139
00:10:08,541 --> 00:10:13,000
- Want a ride?
- It's okay. My parents are coming to get me too.

140
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:16,090
- Hey, my mom really wants to meet you.
- Oh, really?

141
00:10:16,114 --> 00:10:17,914
- Yeah!
- Hey, Tsujitani!

142
00:10:18,019 --> 00:10:20,579
- Hurry up!
- Sorry! Well, see ya.

143
00:10:20,979 --> 00:10:22,000
Ah, sorry, sorry.

144
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:24,110
Sorry to keep you waiting. Let's go.

145
00:10:26,979 --> 00:10:28,459
- Let's go.
- Yeah, let's go.

146
00:10:38,809 --> 00:10:39,809
Watarai, are you okay?

147
00:10:40,590 --> 00:10:41,910
Your phone's not getting service?

148
00:10:42,109 --> 00:10:43,109
Yeah.

149
00:10:43,739 --> 00:10:46,579
The trains stopped running, so I
was going to ask my family for a ride.

150
00:10:47,099 --> 00:10:48,730
Oh, really? Are you all right?

151
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:50,340
Yeah.

152
00:10:50,479 --> 00:10:53,040
It'll probably go through soon.

153
00:10:54,239 --> 00:10:55,239
What about you?

154
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:56,330
Are you okay?

155
00:11:01,590 --> 00:11:03,540
Yeah, um...

156
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:05,919
Hmm?

157
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,200
Well... um...

158
00:11:08,201 --> 00:11:10,400
If you don't mind...

159
00:11:11,599 --> 00:11:12,879
Do you want to come to my place?

160
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:16,880
Huh?
